subject: Volleyball
NCAA Volleyball Championships
lead_paragraph: Megan Courtney and Aiyana Whitney each had 11 kills, and Penn State defeated Brigham Young, 25-21, 26-24, 25-14, in Oklahoma City to win their second consecutive N.C.A.A. women’s volleyball championship.
